attributes.review: I cannot even begin to describe the amount of pain and anger this app has given me. First of all, it took 19 days to download, and that was with the extra boost of a sacrificial ritual to help speed things along. Secondly, when I opened the app it asked for my social security number and let me tell you, I am no longer allowed in 30+ countries after that mistake. Third, after I finally signed up and got into the app, it used my phone number I entered to tell my father that his lack of a back bone is the true reason I go to therapy. Lastly, it charged me $69.99 to be able to look at the app on my screen which I considered a bit rude. DO NOT GET THIS APP! ONLY SUFFERING COMES FROM IT!
